author: Virtual Reality Oasis
description:
The Ready Or Not VRO Mod is launching on Friday Nov 14th 2025! 

This is a passion project I've been working on for some time. This is the most immersive way to play Ready Or Not in VR. The Ready Or Not VRO mod is completely free and it will only work with the Steam version of the game. 

If you want to learn more about the Ready Or Not VRO Mod and how to install it, please join our Discord here; https://t.co/VbHAfb4Kme

You can support the project here; https://ko-fi.com/readyornotvromod

*READY OR NOT AND THE READY OR NOT LOGO ARE TRADEMARKS OR REGISTERED TRADEMARKS OF VOID INTERACTIVE*
